plot: After being with Slade for a year and half, Gretchen still doesn't know if she is ready for marriage again. Vicki heads to Seattle for her annual insurance conference, leaving Donn alone, yet again. Vicki's daughter, Briana, arrives in time for a night of cocktails and bowling, but as the day winds down, Vicki's playful conversation with an employee makes Briana uncomfortable.—Anonymous
